                "invention-title": [
                    "System and method for preparing sodium bicarbonate by capturing carbon dioxide of integrated electric energy feedback system",
                    "一种集成电能回馈系统的捕集二氧化碳制备碳酸氢钠的系统及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a system and a method for preparing sodium bicarbonate by capturing carbon dioxide with low-concentration alkali liquor integrated with an electric energy feedback system, and the main process flow is as follows: brine diaphragm electrolysis is used for preparing alkali, and the obtained dilute alkali liquor is used for capturing and converting carbon dioxide to prepare a sodium bicarbonate product; hydrogen generated by the cathode of the electrolytic bath and chlorine generated by the anode of the electrolytic bath serve as fuel and an oxidizing agent of the hydrogen-chlorine fuel cell respectively, generated electric energy is used for feeding back part of electric power consumed by electrolysis, and meanwhile generated hydrochloric acid is an important chemical and can be sold or used by a user. According to the invention, carbon dioxide is captured and utilized, carbon emission is effectively reduced, sodium and chlorine elements in the raw materials are converted into bulk chemicals, the atom economy is good, and the integrated hydrogen-chlorine fuel cell can feed back part of electrolytic power. According to the method, collaborative recycling and energy regeneration of carbon dioxide and salt are achieved, the method is suitable for capturing and utilizing carbon dioxide in power plant flue gas or carbon-rich tail gas of a chemical plant, and reference is provided for industrial high-concentration brine treatment and waste salt recycling."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种集成电能回馈系统的低浓度碱液捕集二氧化碳制备碳酸氢钠的系统及方法，其主要工艺流程为：将盐水隔膜电解制碱，获得的稀碱液用于二氧化碳的捕集、转化，制备碳酸氢钠产品；电解槽阴极产生的氢气和阳极产生的氯气分别作为氢氯燃料电池的燃料和氧化剂，产生的电能用于回馈电解消耗的部分电力，同时产生的盐酸是一种重要的化学品，可出售或自用。本发明不仅将二氧化碳捕集利用，有效减少碳排放，还将原料中的钠、氯元素转化为大宗化学品，原子经济性好，而且集成的氢氯燃料电池还能回馈部分电解电力。本发明实现了二氧化碳和盐的协同资源化与能源化，适用于电厂烟气或化工厂富碳尾气中二氧化碳的捕集利用，对工业高浓盐水处理和废盐资源化也提供了参考。"
                }
            ]
